  "Line": {
    "Id": "Select",
    "Default": {
      "Id": "Standard",
      "Text": "Even if you don't actually care about growing flowers, you could fetch a decent price for them. Or social clout, if your human friends have any taste in fine botany."
    },
    "MetadataKey": "Gk1_4_1",
    "Options": {
      "Gk1_4-L1": {
        "Id": "Standard",
        "Text": "I recognize that look. Don't worry, black orchids are one of the few Void-touched flowers that aren't dripping with thorns and neurotoxins. Completely safe for animals... though I haven't had the heart to test that with grounded plants."
      },
      "Gk1_4-L2": {
        "Id": "Standard",
        "Text": "Regardless, it would be a shame to let them decay after all I did to get them to this point. Not to mention that it's such a huge taboo for us that even I feel weird about it."
      }
    }
  },
